    "custom_liquid_UhArkr": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div style=\"margin: 24px 0; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin: 16px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;\">Häufig gestellte Fragen</h3>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 1 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Wann werde ich erste Ergebnisse bemerken?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Die meisten Kunden berichten von einer spürbaren Verbesserung der Durchblutung und mehr Wärme in den Extremitäten nach 2–4 Wochen. Für optimale Ergebnisse empfehlen wir eine Mindesteinnahme von 60 Tagen.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 2 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Wie nehme ich Capsaicin Power ein?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Täglich 3–4 Softgels mit einem großen Glas Wasser einnehmen, vorzugsweise zu einer Mahlzeit. Die Softgel-Form sorgt dafür, dass keine Magenreizungen entstehen.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 3 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Verursacht es Sodbrennen oder Magenprobleme?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Nein. Im Gegensatz zu herkömmlichen Cayennepfeffer-Kapseln ist Capsaicin Power in magenschonender Softgel-Form erhältlich und enthält Kurkuma, das Sodbrennen aktiv verhindert. Kein Pfefferaufstoßen, keine Reizungen.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 4 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Ist es sicher für Diabetiker?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Capsaicin Power ist zuckerfrei, glutenfrei und ohne GVO. Viele unserer Kunden sind Diabetiker. Wir empfehlen dennoch, bei der Einnahme von anderen Medikamenten einen Arzt zu konsultieren.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 5 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Warum 60 Tage und nicht 30?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">30-Tages-Produkte werden oft abgebrochen, bevor die Ergebnisse sichtbar werden. Mit 60 Tagen Vorrat pro Beutel stellen wir sicher, dass Sie den vollständigen Reparaturzyklus durchlaufen — und echte, messbare Ergebnisse erleben.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 6 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Was ist Ihre Rückgabegarantie?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Wir bieten eine 60-Tage-Geld-zurück-Garantie. Wenn Sie nicht vollständig zufrieden sind, erstatten wir Ihnen den vollen Kaufpreis — ohne Fragen. Schreiben Sie einfach an support@nelorya.com.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FAQ 7 -->\n  <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n    <button onclick=\"toggleFaq2(this)\" style=\"width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; text-align: left;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#cb4b45\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"9 11 12 14 22 4\"/><path d=\"M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11\"/></svg>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #111;\">Wie lange dauert die Lieferung nach Deutschland?</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg class=\"faq2-arrow\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#6b7280\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"flex-shrink:0;transition:transform 0.2s;\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"/></svg>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"faq2-answer\" style=\"display:none; padding: 0 0 14px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;\">Bestellungen werden innerhalb von 24 Stunden versandt. Die Lieferzeit nach Deutschland beträgt 7–12 Werktage. Der Versand ist kostenlos ab dem ersten Beutel.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq2(btn) {\n    var answer = btn.nextElementSibling;\n    var arrow = btn.querySelector('.faq2-arrow');\n    var isOpen = answer.style.display === 'block';\n    answer.style.display = isOpen ? 'none' : 'block';\n    arrow.style.transform = isOpen ? 'rotate(0deg)' : 'rotate(180deg)';\n  }\n</script>",
